OL,3,CNew compensation scheme announced for
OL,4,CPost Office Capture victims
OL,6,FPostmasters who suffered financial
OL,7,Fshortfalls in the 1990s due to errors
OL,8,Fof the faulty Capture IT system that
OL,9,Fpreceded the Horizon scandal will be
OL,10,Fentitled to payouts from a new redress
OL,11,Fscheme.
OL,13,FCapture, which was a precursor to
OL,14,FHorizon developed in-house by the Post
OL,15,FOffice, led to a number of sub-
OL,16,Fpostmasters being accused of
OL,17,F"accounting malpractice", with some
OL,18,Fhaving their contracts terminated.
OL,20,FSome resigned, while others were
OL,21,Fprosecuted or had to pay money back.
