OL,3,CNew compensation scheme announced for
OL,4,CPost Office Capture victims
OL,6,FIn a move to "right the wrongs of the
OL,7,Fpast", the Department for Business and
OL,8,FTrade has announced a new compensation
OL,9,Fscheme for those affected by the
OL,10,Ffaults of Capture between 1992 and
OL,11,F2000.
OL,13,FIt follows the government's acceptance
OL,14,Fof findings from an independent
OL,15,Finvestigation by Kroll Associates,
OL,16,Fwhich concluded there was a reasonable
OL,17,Flikelihood that Capture created
OL,18,Ffinancial shortfalls for postmasters.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
