OL,3,CNew compensation scheme announced for
OL,4,CPost Office Capture victims
OL,6,FKroll found that 13.5% of all branches
OL,7,Fmay have used Capture, and that sub-
OL,8,Fpostmasters felt pressured by network
OL,9,Fand area managers to use the system.
OL,10,FIts report also found that legal teams
OL,11,Fhad not been investigating potential
OL,12,F"bugs or errors" in the system.
OL,14,FAt least 40 former sub-postmasters
OL,15,Fclaimed they were wrongly accused of
OL,16,Ftheft due to errors in the Capture
OL,17,Fsystem, ITV News reported last year.
