OL,3,CNew compensation scheme announced for
OL,4,CPost Office Capture victims
OL,6,F"Today's announcement represents
OL,7,Fanother important step in righting the
OL,8,Fwrongs of the past and rebuilding
OL,9,Ftrust in the Post Office," said Post
OL,10,FOffice Minister Gareth Thomas.
OL,12,FThe scheme is expected to open for
OL,13,Fapplications in Autumn 2025, with an
OL,14,Finitial phased rollout for 150
OL,15,Fclaimants to ensure the process is
OL,16,Ffair, proportionate and accessible
OL,17,Fbefore wider implementation.
