OL,3,CNew compensation scheme announced for
OL,4,CPost Office Capture victims
OL,6,FIt comes as the government confirmed
OL,7,Fthat #1 billion has been paid out in
OL,8,Fcompensation to over 7,300 postmasters
OL,9,Faffected by the Horizon IT scandal,
OL,10,Fand the opening of the Horizon
OL,11,FShortfalls Scheme Appeal process in
OL,12,FMay.
OL,14,FThe Capture Redress Scheme has been
OL,15,Fdesigned to address cases dating back
OL,16,Fover two decades, where documentation
OL,17,Fthat can be used as evidence may be
OL,18,Flimited.
