OL,3,CNew compensation scheme announced for
OL,4,CPost Office Capture victims
OL,6,FIt will include a " straightforward
OL,7,Ftwo-stage process", according to the
OL,8,Fgovernment, comprising of an initial
OL,9,Feligibility review followed by an
OL,10,Findependent panel assessment.
OL,12,FA "holistic" approach to assessments
OL,13,Fwill be taken, considering both
OL,14,Ffinancial losses and the wider
OL,15,Fpersonal impact on postmasters.
