OL,4,CPost Office Capture victims
OL,6,FThe government says the scheme will
OL,7,Falso include prompt preliminary
OL,8,Fpayments for eligible claimants,
OL,9,Fensuring early acknowledgement of
OL,10,Floss, and a guided scoring and banding
OL,11,Fmodel for "consistency in awards,
OL,12,Fwhile maintaining flexibility".
OL,14,FHudgell Solicitors says it is acting
OL,15,Fon behalf of more than 100 former sub-
OL,16,Fpostmasters prosecuted, sacked or made
OL,17,Fto pay back alleged branch shortfalls
OL,18,Fwhen using the Capture accounting
OL,19,Fsystem.
