OL,3,CNew compensation scheme announced for
OL,4,CPost Office Capture victims
OL,6,FFollowing a meeting with the
OL,7,Fgovernment in February to discuss the
OL,8,Fsecond Post Office IT scandal, Neil
OL,9,FHudgell, of Hudgell Solicitors, said:
OL,10,F"We will get redress and justice for
OL,11,Fthose whose lives were affected by
OL,12,FCapture.
OL,14,F"There are potentially hundreds
OL,15,Faffected, and sadly a large number are
OL,16,Flikely to be people who are no longer
OL,17,Fwith us, and died without ever being
OL,18,Fable to clear their name.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
